headline: WWE® Announces Acquisition of Leading Mexican Lucha Libre Promotion AAA
summary: STAMFORD, Conn., April 21, 2025--WWE, part of TKO Group Holdings (NYSE: TKO), has announced its acquisition of leading Mexican lucha libre promotion AAA in partnership with Mexico-based sports and entertainment holding company, Fillip.
